| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2463 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0ebf7182-c99f-5330-b1b3-c33ea0d7993b"
